## 5) Draft issue system (user-facing planner diagnostics)

## File: `lib/planner/draft.ts`

Main role:
Translate raw plan outputs into understandable issues and quick actions.

Key function:
- `buildPlanIssues(...)`
  - emits critical/warning items such as:
    - no usable days
    - unscheduled sessions
    - impossible topic windows
    - late sessions
    - unstable daily load
  - each issue can include:
    - root cause data
    - inline editable constraint fields
    - one-click actions (date delta, constraint delta, jump phase)

Why this matters:
Users can fix plans without reading engine code.

