## 6) Data mapping layer (from DB rows to engine units)

## File: `app/actions/planner/plan.ts`

Important mapping behavior:
- Tasks are source of effort minutes (sum of manual task durations per topic).
- Topic params provide timing rules (session length, dependencies, start/deadline).
- Subject-level deadline can fallback when topic deadline missing.
- Generated session title can be mapped back to underlying task titles for user-friendly preview.

This file is where most real-world bugs happen when requirements change, because it joins many tables and transforms data.

